longBusinessSummary: The fund is an actively managed ETF that seeks broad-equity market exposure, as well as exposure to certain individual equity securities while also employing an options overlay strategy (via risk-defined options) to seek to limit potential losses and to generate additional income. It will invest, under normal circumstances, at least 80% of its net assets plus the amount of borrowings for investment purposes, in the fund’s Core Capital Appreciation Strategy and Options Strategy.
longName: Unity Wealth Partners Dynamic Capital Appreciation & Options ETF
